snippet.title: Anyone’s Diary - Launch Trailer [VR, PlayStation VR]
snippet.description:
Launch trailer for Anyone’s Diary, a third-person virtual reality puzzle-platformer where you discover the story of the character Anyone and help them by solving inner conflicts represented by puzzles. The game is being developed by World Domination Project and will be released for PlayStation VR on January 31, 2019. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/anyones-diary
